Kenya Commercial Bank Directors Quit Amid Reorganization, Bus. Daily Says

-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 
2011-06-06T03:53:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/kenya-commercial-bank-directors-quit-amid-reorganization-bus-daily-says.html
Kenya Commercial Bank Ltd. (KNCB)  said eight
divisional directors have left the company after it cut the
number of people on its executive committee, Business Daily
reported, citing a statement from the company.  Among those who left include a former deputy chief
executive officer and the directors for marketing, mortgages,
 information technology , retail, finance, special projects and
corporate communication, the Nairobi-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Tim Smith  at 
 tsmith58@bloomberg.net  